Class PartSection

java.lang.Object
  com.myronmarston.music.notation.AbstractNotationElement

All Implemented Interfaces:
NotationElement
public class PartSection
extends AbstractNotationElement

Represents one section of a notation part. This is necessary to allow different sections to have different key signatures.
